<br>
    I don't want to turn off sigs.  I like sigs.  Many are beautiful.  I do think that some are overly sexy (yes, I know that the poster who uses one is a person, has genitals, and presumable knows what to do with them... why should I care about that?)  But having a formalized board approved formula of what is or is not allowed in sigs?  That has overtones of goosesteping, brown shirts, and straight arm salutes to me.<br>
<br>
    I dunno.  I guess I would vote to let the present system of having the mods decide on a case by case basis stand. <p>-- <br>
