<br>
All signatures will be represented by dots (&quot;.&quot;), and henceforth no actual images shall be displayed.<br>
<br>
One dot (&quot;.&quot;) shall represent a rated &quot;G&quot; picture (kittens, puppies, and domokuns in non sexually suggestive poses)<br>
Two Dots (&quot;..&quot;) shall be used when representing beachwear nudity, and or bloodless violence<br>
Three Dots (&quot;...&quot;) Shall be used when the image represented contains suggestive sexual overtones, hetero, or homosexual. Some violence, and/or any kind of partial nudity.<br>
Four Dots (&quot;....&quot;) are not allowed under any circumstances. Anyone posting four dots (&quot;....&quot;) shall be IP banned, then tracked down, and their house shall be egged and toilet papered thoroughly.<br>
<br>
Thank you for supporting the new standards and I look forward to a peaceful and prosperous reign as your community Emperor.<br>
<br>
